title: Rewind to MGK Interview and More
itunes:title: Rewind to MGK Interview and More
description:
Thursday 12/20 - Today on the show we flashed back to when MGK stopped by during his beef with Eminem and G- Eazy and he definitely didn't hold anything back! Also, since it is Thursday we flashed back to the most memorable Ask Yee's and a flash back to when Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Ronnie from Jersey Shore.
